Package com.SCHSRobotics.HAL9001.system.subsystems

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MechanumDrive
    A built in mechanum drive class with 7 drive modes.
    MechanumDrive.Params
    A parameter class for passing all desired options into mechanum drive.
    MechanumDrive.SpecificParams
    A class used for entering necessary params while in config mode or for using more specific versions of params than can be set with the config.
    OmniWheelDrive
    A built in OmniWheel drive class with 7 drive modes.
    OmniWheelDrive.Params
    A parameter class for passing all desired options into OmniWheel drive.
    OmniWheelDrive.SpecificParams
    A class used for entering necessary params while in config mode or for using more specific versions of params than can be set with the config.
    QuadWheelDrive
    A customizable tankdrive subsystem.
    QuadWheelDrive.NumberParams
    A parameters class that is used to pass options into the drive system when config is being used but you want specific values for certain numbers.
    QuadWheelDrive.Params
    A parameters class that is used to pass options into the drive system.
    TankDrive
    A customizable tankdrive subsystem.
    TankDrive.NumberParams
    A parameters class used when you need to pass specific numbers into the drive but still want to use config.
    TankDrive.Params
    A parameters class used to pass parameters to the drive.
